author: reinhard
msg: the previous solution only wrote to the console after the first 'update' event had arrived. In practice this will mostly be good enough but if your first change is a 'create' event, it doesn't appear.
this fix turns on console output when the first servlet or filter is called.

author: trustin
msg: Resolved issue: DIRMINA-545 - Make ConnectFuture ready right after sessionCreated
* Changed DefaultIoFilterChain to call ConnectFuture.setSession() right after IoHandler.sessionCreated() is invoked.
